{
  "stem": "1338.5",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was one event what I failed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I would not want to discuss it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Probably-- whether I brought my boss to a job, or whether I had some food [SIGHS] that I could share.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Once in a while I worked in a-- in peeling potatoes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We'd steal potatoes together with the Russians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But then I got in a clique with the Russians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I didn't help somebody I should have helped, because I was afraid that the Russians will, you know, disown me, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Look, it's not an easy-- this is not-- you know-- you know, I don't have the luxury-- I didn't have the luxury, neither age-wise, experience-wise-- remember I was 19 years old-- that I could afford this contemplation in-- in such a terrible environment as that.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I just-- I'm trying to excuse myself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "No, I didn't do anything terrible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I have a clear conscious.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I've never done anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I have probably been a good friend, and a loyal-- a loyal comrade.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But you wish you did more.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There were instances which I wish back I did more.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I did Serge too in, not willingly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "After reading Solzhenitsyn, I know where he wound up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was the-- I was the-- the-- I was the [SIGHS] Count Bezukhov vis-a-vis my poor Russian peasant I was playing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I don't want to play the game.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I was-- I loved him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But I said to him, look, you are a stupid peasant.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You don't understand anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I am the educated person.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I read Marx, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I know everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He says to me, Max, you realize you have a number, at least.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I come back to Russia, they will shoot me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I says, what are you talking about?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
